column4: Virginia auto dealer group sues Tesla to stop 2nd store in state
column5: DETROIT The Virginia Automobile Dealers Association (VADA) on Wednesday filed a lawsuit against Tesla Motors Inc and Virginia state officials to keep the electric car maker from opening a second dealership in the state.
